<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Login Alert</title>
        <style>
        * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    }

    body {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: aliceblue;
    }

    .container {
        width: 25em;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: solid 1px rgb(189, 184, 184);
        padding: 5px;
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        justify-content: center;
        place-items: center;
    }

    .image_holder {
        width: 6em;
        height: 6em;
        border-radius: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        place-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: solid 1px rgb(189, 184, 184);
    }

    .image_holder .img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .article_container {
        width: 100%;
        margin-left: 5px;
        margin-right: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        place-items: center;
        font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .article_container .greating {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .article_container .greating .name {
        font-weight: bolder;
    }

    .content_container {
        text-align: center;
        color: rgb(46, 45, 45);
    }

    .main_link {
        width: fit-content;
        padding: 2px 10px;
        background-color: #f57e16;
        border-radius: 3px;
        justify-self: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
    }

    .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: rgb(88, 88, 88);
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {{!-- the container --}}
    <div class="container">
        {{!-- the image holder --}}
        <div class="image_holder">
            {{!-- the image --}}
            <img src="https://www.creativefabrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Restaurant-Logo-by-Koko-Store-580x386.jpg" class="img" alt="">
        </div>
         {{!-- the article container --}}
        <div class="article_container">
            {{!-- the greatting --}}
            <div class="greating">
                Hi <span>{{name}},</span>
            </div>
            {{!-- the subject --}}
            <div class="subject">
                <p>We are trying to reach you that user is loged in by your account.</p>
            </div>
            {{!-- the content --}}
            <div class="content_container">
                <p>Are you really you that you loged to admin account?.</p>
                <p class="company_description">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iste tempora officiis ab facere voluptatum magnam sed blanditiis exercitationem non maiores.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- the conclusion --}}
        <div class="footer">
            <span>&copy;</span> C5 Online Caffe 2015 E.C
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>